snippet.title: AVSEQ: Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
AVSEQ is now available on Steam! http://store.steampowered.com/app/207670/

AVSEQ is our audio-visual sequencer puzzle game with 2.2300745198530623×10^43 possible audio permutations, thats 22 tredecillion in total! It's very pretty, and fun to play.
